{"tid":1850811,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個武漢肺炎改變左你嘅嘢","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:45:32.000Z","uid":43786,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"296a697126c1b13646fe8fa2c12a9dd465dbdfcf","tid":1850811,"uid":43786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:18:26.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n返到屋企嘅衫褲會當晚即開機洗<br />\n唔會著第二次<br />\n以前冬天d長褲都會著兩日<br />\n而家連外套都係一次即洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0707e92a091f5ecaacbde743f72a3c6e03c09274","tid":1850811,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e78147a425d5eb65db905786682b8fc20bb66da","tid":1850811,"uid":33452,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"多左同老竇講野  <br />\n而老竇又多左接納我講既野"},{"pid":"a06f4933b6834ab8a2e6ada1ad939e5f04e1e7dd","tid":1850811,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"對祖國認同感大左"},{"pid":"f634596ae565ccac0880aea99a53adfe64697dac","tid":1850811,"uid":125090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a06f4933b6834ab8a2e6ada1ad939e5f04e1e7dd","tid":1850811,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":40,"score":-38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:25:10.000Z","msg":"對祖國認同感大左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262041e5b3986b58b7e1ce55dcb66d3d12d3e1c0","tid":1850811,"uid":43786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8e78147a425d5eb65db905786682b8fc20bb66da","tid":1850811,"uid":33452,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"多左同老竇講野  <br />\n而老竇又多左接納我講既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:53:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎唯一帶黎嘅好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01398e9dbc7a49376ab7253d191fb12c66e77406","ti